s/normal/devil.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"833df78abaefb07908e444055bdfe013d4bd92fd","tid":165450,"uid":42449,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-03-30T11:02:27.000Z","msg":"lm"},{"pid":"2f36a537b6abccc0a828c7c1eda926296746d1bf","tid":165450,"uid":68160,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-04-03T10:53:17.000Z","msg":"<span style=\"font-size: large;\">蘋果新聞</span>報導：<br />\n<br />\n<a href=\"http://hk.apple.nextmedia.com/news/art/20160611/19650221?_ga=1.81682135.1598945194.1417291085\" data-sr-url=\"https://r.lihkg.com/link?u=http%3A%2F%2Fhk.apple.nextmedia.com%2Fnews%2Fart%2F20160611%2F19650221%3F_ga%3D1.81682135.1598945194.1417291085&d=ZEuQNtRgUz7rCGSUvjEm926kGZraZVKwHE52VSkiKoI%3D&h=4b0f3047\" data-ef-url=\"https://embed.lih.kg/frame?u=http%3A%2F%2Fhk.apple.nextmedia.com%2Fnews%2Fart%2F20160611%2F19650221%3F_ga%3D1.81682135.1598945194.1417291085&h=c7a6dc83\" data-auto-link target=\"_blank\">http://hk.apple.nextmedia.com/news/art/20160611/19650221?_ga=1.81682135.1598945194.1417291085</a>"},{"pid":"a103bbfd17113d8254668e1fc0f4d274798ec57e","tid":165450,"uid":68160,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-04-05T10:45:04.000Z","msg":"政府資助"},{"pid":"edab51bb088084cff73837ccc4f32f2f7308a132","tid":165450,"uid":68160,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-04-11T06:57:23.000Z","msg":"DSE 科目"},{"pid":"0ed6371dc06c778397ecc5604f9284ef81ac53a5","tid":165450,"uid":17051,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-04-11T07:01:55.000Z","msg":"一句話有參考外國網站 之後再由老師指導 自行設計就當釋出疑慮 未免太過兒戲"},{"pid":"54ef58f2dd787a69f7327f72dfa969af58f0c34e","tid":165450,"uid":69778,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-04-11T07:53:28.000Z","msg":"<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/angel.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"}]}